@startuml
skinparam dpi 150

participant Sender
participant "Hash Function" as H
participant "Sign\n(Private Key)" as SIG
participant "Verify\n(Public Key)" as VER
participant Receiver

Sender -> H : message
H --> SIG : hash(message)
SIG --> Sender : signature
Sender --> Receiver : message + signature

Receiver -> H : message  \n(extracted from received data)
H --> Receiver : hash(message)
Receiver -> VER : signature + hash(message)
VER --> Receiver : valid / invalid

@enduml
